Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.64,0:00:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\bord0\fad(1000,500)\pos(189,178)}编剧：托比·怀特豪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,按照传统\N{\fs14}Traditionally,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,革命总是始于一声枪响\N{\fs14}Revolutions begin with a gun shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,或者战斗的号角\N{\fs14}Or a call to arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是当未来历史学家们回顾往昔\N{\fs14}but when future historians look back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找卡勒的黄金时代的萌芽时\N{\fs14}to find the seed of the golden age of the Kahler.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们发现它始于这里\N{\fs14}They see it began here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.60,0:00:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,始于此时\N{\fs14}began now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,始于一个想法\N{\fs14}began now, with an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,意图在于创造一种活武器\N{\fs14}The intention is to create a living weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一台全方位的战争机器\N{\fs14}A multifaceted war machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,永不疲倦 永不故障\N{\fs14}that doesn't tire, doesn't malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,实验对象选自于我们最后剩余的军校\N{\fs14}The subjects were chosen from our last remaining military academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们必须足够健康强壮\N{\fs14}As they have to be healthy and resilient enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,才能在改造过程中存活\N{\fs14}to survive the procedures.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.98,0:00:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一定程度的欺骗是必要的\N{\fs14}A degree of duplicity was necessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了保证有人愿意参与\N{\fs14}to secure their participation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只知道自己被选中成为\N{\fs14}They were told they've been selected for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,外星殖民地的维和机器\N{\fs14}peace keeping machines on off-world colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的武器 雷达 和芯片\N{\fs14}All weaponry, radar and intel,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,都要完全焊接在宿主身上\N{\fs14}will be literally fused with the host.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,使得士兵和武器融为一体\N{\fs14}So the soldier and artillery are one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,六号实验对象\N{\fs14}Sunbject 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,卡勒-铁克\N{\fs14}Kahler-Tek
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,想法成为了现实\N{\fs14}The idea made flesh.
